OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBright spells and blustery showers
OL,7,Fcontinue through Thursday. A further
OL,8,Frain band pushes northeast on Friday,
OL,9,Fshowers follow later. Bright spells
OL,10,Fand showers again on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
